name: My rainbow
description:
from the collection "inside:lights"

The sky is mine
The sun is mine
If it rains, all the raindrops are mine
Even the rainbow is mine
Lands, seas, stars
Clouds, moon and all the trees of all the forests
And all the singing birds
I call everyone by my own name
everything
every where
And then I give it all to you
Even my rainbow ...
